The '''Rebel Command Fleet''' was the main force of the [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Alliance Fleet]] and fought at the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]. Prior to the battle, it gathered at [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]] with the [[Sullustan Home Guard/Legends|Sullustan Home Guard]]. The fleet numbered hundreds of small vessels supported by at least forty [[MC80 Star Cruiser/Legends|MC80 Star Cruisers]].

